Description_lang: Uploads the Orange Spraybot blueprint to Pascal-K1N6, allowing you to craft it through Junkyard Tinkering.

description_blz.en_US: Uploads the Orange Spraybot blueprint to Pascal-K1N6, allowing you to craft it through Junkyard Tinkering.

description_blz.ko_KR: 주황색 분무로봇 도면을 파스칼-ㄷH오5에 업로드합니다. 고철 작업장 땜질을 통해 제작할 수 있습니다.
